---
title: Plant-Based Chick'n Tenders & Israeli Couscous Medley  with Golden Pumpkin & Plant-Based Basil Pesto Mayo
description: Quick and easy, that’s the best kind of dinner. Roast the pumpkin in our Aussie spice blend then whip up a fluffy
couscous and have it ready to be gobbled down in no time at all. Top it off with a plant-based basil pesto mayo to ensure there won’t be any crumbs left.
